{"tid":506364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩漢闖機舖 刀劈釣魚機增值機","createTime":"2017-12-22T06:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T06:46:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"797e51b65a5fba2c1667892110c318e814692f2a","tid":506364,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513915476_376b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513915476_376b.jpg&h=9c5924e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌和宜合道一間遊戲機中心，上午10時半，兩名男子突然闖入，一人負責「睇水」，另一人持刀亂劈，砸毀一部增值機及一部釣魚機，職員喝止及報警。警方趕至時兩名歹徒已逃去無蹤，警方列刑事毀壞案，正翻查閉路電視錄影，追緝歹徒歸案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171222/57613167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57613167&d=LX3jfKltR5G0quaevRKfHDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8962493d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57613167&h=0aa0e8d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171222/57613167</a>"},{"pid":"b6690951e7a123dd8338010b64fe4cc0df40e8b3","tid":506364,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n低智力罪犯"},{"pid":"ee94519b46d24c63ce31ee1234c1abe0900b01a7","tid":506364,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肯定打魚打到輸左好多"}]}